1. Učiteljica je učenicima objasnila bojenje* jesenjih listova. (The teacher explained to the students how to color the autumn leaves.)

2. Bojenje* zida treba da bude kvalitetno. (The wall painting should be of good quality.)

3. Boji* se da će uspeti da završi projekat. (She is afraid that she won't be able to finish the project.)

4. Bojenje* noktiju je postalo popularno. (Painting nails has become popular.)

5. Boji* se da će biti kažnjen. (He is afraid of being punished.)